<concept id="whr-topic-page-layout">
  <title>WebHelp Responsive Topic Page</title>
  <conbody>
    <p id="publication-toc">The main function of this page is to presents the topic's content in the
      central part. Besides this, you can use the <xref
        keyref="whr-topic-page-layout/publication-toc">publication TOC</xref> or <xref
        keyref="whr-topic-page-layout/publication-menu">menu component</xref> to find other topics
      or <xref keyref="whr-topic-page-layout/search-query-input">search query input</xref> to search
      in the documentation.</p>
    <?oxy_comment_start author="radu" timestamp="20180210T180525+0200" comment="TODO - A screenshot with footer"?>
