      <title>Topic Page Components</title>
      <p>The layout components displayed in this page are:</p>
      <p>
        <dl>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-webhelp-layout-reusable/publication-title" id="publication-title">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-webhelp-layout-reusable/main-page-logo" id="main-page-logo">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-webhelp-layout-reusable/publication-menu" id="publication-menu">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-webhelp-layout-reusable/index-terms-link" id="index-terms-link">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-webhelp-layout-reusable/search-query-input" id="search-query-input">
            <dt/>
            <dd/>
          </dlentry>
          
          <dlentry id="main-page-tiles">
            <dt>Topic Content</dt>
            <dd>Presents the content of the associated DITA topic.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry id="main-page-tile">
            <dt>Breadcrumb</dt>
            <dd>Presents the path of the current displayed DITA topic in documentation.</dd>
          </dlentry>          
          <dlentry id="topic-title">
            <dt>Publication TOC</dt>
            <dd>A Table of Content for the publication.</dd>
          </dlentry>
          <dlentry conkeyref="reusables-webhelp-layout-reusable/main-page-footer" id="main-page-footer">
